summary: Fable\\\\\\\'s Forge is an online mod development manager that allows modders to manage the development of their new and existing mods.
descriptionHtml:
Fable\\\\\\\'s Forge is an online mod development manager that allows modders to manage the development of their new and existing mods.  The Mod Development Interface allows users to design, develop, and create new mods.  In essence it is a project manager that allows team leaders to organize milestones, set and assign tasks, and track progress and time in an effort to create a well-organized mod.

The resource can be found at [url=http://www.fablesforge.com]Fable\'s Forge[/url].

Note: You must register to utilize the resource.
author: Fables Forge
